title: Eagles, Eli Manning, Aaron Rodgers, UFC 229, and the Cowboys
itunes:title: Eagles, Eli Manning, Aaron Rodgers, UFC 229, and the Cowboys
description:
Colin discusses the continued fall of the Philadelphia Eagles, why the New York Giants need to move on from QB Eli Manning, the poor play of Green Bay Packers QB Aaron Rodgers, his thoughts on the aftermath of Conor McGregor vs. Khabib Nurmagomedov at UFC 229, and the backlash Dallas Cowboys HC Jason Garrett is receiving. Guests include Michael Vick, Greg Jennings, Trent Dilfer, and Tony Gonzalez.
